`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Nexus
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'nexus' <target>

 This spell is virtually identical to portal (see 'help portal'), with the
difference being that while portal creates a unidirectional gateway, a nexus 
spell makes a two-sided gateway. It also lasts longer than the lower-powered
portal spell.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
